Yanqiu, check this again.

33
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,560
Three, two...

34
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,160
Meet the requirements of the bank.

35
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,000
Chunsheng.

36
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,960
Oh, everyone's here.

37
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,440
Let me tell you some good news.

38
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:06,240
We've got Jingxi Hospital's order!

39
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,160
- Yeah!
- Great!

40
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:08,680
Congratulations!

41
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,600
And we're the main agent.

42
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:12,320
Many departments of Jingxi Hospital

43
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:14,280
will adopt our instruments.

44
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,560
Wonderful!

45
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:18,120
Yanqiu, look. The contract.

46
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,280
The deposit will be paid soon.

47
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,720
Most importantly,

48
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,640
I can pay out wages immediately!

49
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,520
Yeah, wages!

50
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,120
It's the day we've been expecting.

51
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,600
Wages!

52
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,160
Well, my treat.

53
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,520
Let's go have dinner.

54
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,920
Chunsheng, I'll tell you what.

55
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,160
We'll order a lot of food this time.

56
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,320
