57
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,120
- Go.
- Go.

58
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,640
Qi Tian.

59
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,000
Oh, Yanqiu.

60
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:43,920
What's wrong?

61
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,640
Send me to the hospital.

62
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:56,620
(Gynecology and Obstetrics
Operating Room)

63
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:08,960
Tian.

64
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,040
Congratulations. Your wife
gave birth to a daughter.

65
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,440
Thank you, doctor.

66
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:14,680
Thank you.

67
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:18,950
Tian, congratulations!

68
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,120
I have a daughter?

69
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:21,880
