841
00:42:15,560 --> 00:42:16,840
If your brother hadn't despised me,

842
00:42:17,080 --> 00:42:19,000
he wouldn't have punched me
irresponsibly.

843
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:20,840
And your parents.

844
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:22,960
They wouldn't have given me
a hard time just for trifles.

845
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:24,120
Even Xiao Chunsheng,

846
00:42:24,520 --> 00:42:25,520
if he hadn't despised me,

847
00:42:26,040 --> 00:42:27,280
he wouldn't have embarrassed me
in front of our leaders

848
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:28,880
and put me on the spot.

849
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:30,880
I'd like to ask you, Ye Fang.

850
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:32,800
Are you guys just selfish

851
00:42:33,320 --> 00:42:35,600
